{
  "stem": "2684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we-- we didn't have to-- we didn't had to be sheltered from the outside life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And because of that, we were too busy to living our childhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't thought much about what we going to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't have an aim, because those days, nobody had an-- an aim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It-- it wasn't a life as advanced as today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You could not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] plan to the future so far, because happenings in the world started getting so fast, and-- and-- and positions, and-- and-- and things change so quickly in political ways.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But in another way, a family, they're born in the same place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They lived in the same place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and in my eyes, they died in the same place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was no-- no-- it was no wandering Jews in my time, that we went from suburbs to suburbs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My grandmother lived in the place where we lived, my father lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I thought I'm going to live in the same place when I grow old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if-- if I am a-- won't-- won't be able enough to-- to start some-- some diplomatic-- I'm sorry-- not diplomatic-- yeah-- diplomatic career-- by that, I mean, if I don't have a diploma of some sort of, I'm going to take over my father's or my mother's business, and-- and live happily ever after.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The future wasn't a-- a great importance to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first sign of danger-- the first time of danger started to me in-- in 1944, after the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That I'm not very familiar with the exact dates, but I'm familiar with exact times, and that's two different things.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
